This product uses YashanDB technologies, including but not limited to:
- YashanDB 23.5.4+ (崖山数据库)
- YashanDB VECTOR data type + HNSW vector index
- YashanDB SEARCH INDEX (full-text search)
- YashanDB JSON type
- YashanDB PL/SQL packages (Memory Fusion, Knowledge Base API, ...)
- YashanDB DBMS_SCHEDULER (scheduled jobs)
- yaspy 1.2.1 (Python driver for YashanDB)

